### ðŸ“Š CSV vs JSON: Use Case Comparison

| Use Case                   | CSV     | JSON        |
|----------------------------|---------|-------------|
| Tabular data (rows/columns)| âœ… Yes  | âŒ Not Ideal|
| Nested/structured data     | âŒ No   | âœ… Yes      |
| API communication          | âŒ Rare | âœ… Standard |
| Editable in Excel          | âœ… Easy | âŒ Hard     |
| Configs/settings files     | âŒ No   | âœ… Common   |
| Small databases/storage    | âœ… Simpler | âœ… Flexible |
